 BARBERTON – No charges were levelled against Mark Norris (39) this morning. Luke Von Johnston and John Ntimane were killed in a shooting incident at Boondock Farm on Tuesday.  According to police spokesman, Norris spent the night in police custody. He was escorted to the Barberton Magistrate’s Court this morning.   Norris left court without being charged. NPA Spokesman Monica Nyuswa said “There is at this stage not enough admissible evidence on the docket to warrant the matter to be enrolled.”   